        "title": {
            "rendered": "Step 1:  What are savings?"
        },
        "content": {
            "rendered": "\n<p><strong><em>Savings</em></strong> is the money that you earned that you put aside for a future goal.<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>What do you want to accomplish in the future? Do you want to build an emergency fund? Do you want to pay for your child‚Äôs education? Do you need to get out of debt? Do you want to buy a plot of land?&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It‚Äôs important to define your goals. Your goals will influence the choices you make when you are creating your budget.</p>\n\n\n\n<p></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>What do you want to save for?&nbsp;</strong><br>Share in the comments below! <br></p>\n",
            "protected": false
        },
