        "link": "https://community.tala.test/course/design-a-business-idea/lessons/step-6-refine-your-idea/",
        "title": {
            "rendered": "Step 6: Refine your idea"
        },
        "content": {
            "rendered": "\n<p>If your potential customers were not excited about your idea, don‚Äôt be discouraged! Take what you learned from your potential customers and refine your business idea. Adjust it so that it will meet the needs of your potential customers. Feel free to get feedback as many times as you feel comfortable before starting your business. It‚Äôs easy to change your business when it‚Äôs just an idea. It is much harder after you‚Äôve invested a lot of time or money into starting it!&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>If your potential customers were enthusiastic, then you are ready to start making a business plan!</p>\n\n\n\n<h3>What&#8217;s your business idea? </h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Tell us in the comments below! <br></p>\n",
            "protected": false
        },
