        "title": {
            "rendered": "Step 7: Understanding your revenue stream"
        },
        "content": {
            "rendered": "\n<p>A<strong> revenue stream</strong> is how your business earns money. You need to understand the following to determine exactly what your revenue stream is:&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Customer Segments:</strong> Who are your customers?</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Channels</strong>: How do you reach your customers?&nbsp;</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Customer Relationships</strong>: How do you get, keep, and grow your customer base?<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p>Defining these will enable you to understand all the ways that money comes <strong>into</strong> your business.&nbsp;<br></p>\n",
            "protected": false
        },
