        "status": "publish",
        "type": "sfwd-lessons",
        "link": "https://community.tala.test/course/build-a-business-model/lessons/step-8-an-example-stanleys-inputs-to-his-revenue-stream/",
        "title": {
            "rendered": "Step 8: An example: Stanley‚Äôs inputs to his revenue stream"
        },
        "content": {
            "rendered": "\n<p>Stanley‚Äôs inputs are:&nbsp;<br></p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Customer Segments: Who are his customers?¬†</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Residents of Rongai&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Channels: How does he reach his customers?¬†</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Social media&nbsp;</li><li>Word of mouth&nbsp;</li><li>Posters + stickers&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Customer Relationships: How does he get, keep and grow his customer base?¬†</strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Providing small samples to passer bys&nbsp;</li><li>Loyalty program + punch card. For customers who have purchased 11 juices, their 12th juice is free&nbsp;</li><li>Providing friendly and reliable service for every customer&nbsp;</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"354\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https://community.tala.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/BusinessModel-600pxW-Step04-354x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-442\" srcset=\"https://community.tala.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/BusinessModel-600pxW-Step04-354x1024.jpg 354w, https://community.tala.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/BusinessModel-600pxW-Step04-104x300.jpg 104w, https://community.tala.test/wp-content/uploads/2019/08/BusinessModel-600pxW-Step04.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 354px) 100vw, 354px\" /></figure>\n",
            "protected": false
        },
